Edit Data Model Object Properties

You can edit data model object (DMO) properties either on the Data Model tab or on the data-mapping canvas.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
In Data Cloud, go to the Data Model tab.
Open your DMO, and click Edit.
Modify any of these properties: Object Label, Object Description, Field Label, or Enable Value Suggestion.
To modify the category of a DMO, see Change the Category of a Data Model Object.

The Enable Value Suggestion option is available only for Text data type fields.

Save your changes.
You can also edit the DMO properties directly from the data-mapping canvas by clicking the Edit Properties icon.
